  "code": "flowchart TB\n\ncve[\"CVE reported\"]\ninvestigate[Check package version with fix]\nimport{Directly imported\npackage}\nmajor{\"Package resolution\nversion increase\"}\npatchMajor[[Supress and raise a ticket]]\npatchMinor[[\"Update package(s) and test\"]]\nchildren[Investigate yarn.lock to find imported packages]\nchildUpdate{\"Do containing packages\nhave minor/patch versions \nwith the fix?\"}\nchildMajor[[Add resolution, test and raise a ticket]]\n\ncve --> investigate\ninvestigate --> major\nimport -- Yes --> patchMinor\nmajor -- \"Major update\" --> patchMajor\nmajor -- \"Minor or patch update\" --> import\nimport -- No --> children\nchildren --> childUpdate\nchildUpdate -- Yes --> patchMinor\nchildUpdate -- No --> childMajor",
